Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,立派になって。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,훌륭해졌어요.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was splendid!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:51.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、おいら、武芸大会で優勝しただス。ジパングナンバー1の武芸者になっただス！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:51.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,응, 나, 무예 대회에서 우승했소! 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되었소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:51.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes! I won the first place at the competition-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I've became the number one martial artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おめでとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,축하해요.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Comment: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルちゃん。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru...
Comment: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ばかもん！夢も早いわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멍청한 것! 꿈을 꾸기에도 이르다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,You idiot! You're even dreaming too early!
Comment: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,悪夢だス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,으악! 악몽이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それ、おいらのコテツでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그건 내 코테츠이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Those are my Kotetsus!
Comment: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,返すだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,돌려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give those back-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだスか、こんなことを。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오, 이런 짓을...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's with this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,アカンベェだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,메롱이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Pfft!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,야!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,怒っただス！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,화났소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,You made me mad-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Comment: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,逃がさんだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,달아날 생각 접으시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,You aren't going anywhere-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何度も同じ手にかかんないだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,또 같은 수에 넘어가지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm not falling over that again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:39.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、この間までこういうことをやってたおいらだス。山の中じゃ負けないでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:39.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 순간까지 이런 일을 한 나인데, 산속이라면 지지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:39.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've been doing that for the whole time; you shall not defeat me in a mountain-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,観念して刀を返すだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,순순히 칼을 돌려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give it up and give my swords back-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なかなかやるだスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's pretty good-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いやいやいや、感心している場合じゃないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니아니, 감탄할 때가 아니오.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, it's not the time to be surprised-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どこへ行っただス？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어디에 갔소?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where did he go-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,出て来いだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come out!
Comment: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,隠れるなんてずるいだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,숨다니 치사하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hiding is unfair-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どこだスか！出て来いだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어디이오! 나오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where are you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?! Show yourself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거기!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right there!
Comment: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何するだス。ちょちょ、ちょっと待っただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 짓이오! 잠깐 멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}? Stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いきなり切りかかるなんて卑怯なことは許さんだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,갑자기 들이대다니 비겁하고 용서할 수 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Attacking all of a sudden is cowardly and unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何？卑怯だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라? 비겁하다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? Cowardly?
